texts.content: {"text":"2. Bu kitobning nozil qilinishi \nAziyz va o`ta hikmatli Allohdandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"4. Va sizlarning yaratilishingizda va \ntaratib qo`yilgan jonivorlarda aniq ishonadigan qavm uchun oyat(belgi)lar bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,117]}]}

{"text":"5. Kechayu kunduzning almashib turishida, \nAlloh osmondan rizq nozil qilib, uning ila yerni o`limidan keyin tiriltirishida va shamollarning yo`nalishida \naql yuritadigan qavm uchun oyat(belgi)lar bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,200]}]}

{"text":"6. Bular Allohning oyatlaridir. 
Biz ularni senga haq ila tilovat qilurmiz. 
Ular Allohni va Uning oyatlarini qo`yib, 
qaysi gapga iymon keltirurlar?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,150]}]}

{"text":"8. U o`ziga tilovat qilingan \nAllohning oyatlarini eshitadi-yu, so`ngra, \nxuddi eshitmagandek, mutakabbirlik qilib turib olur. Bas, unga alamli azob xushxabarini ber.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,166]}]}

{"text":"9. Qachonki Bizning oyatlarimizdan biror narsa bilsa, uni istehzo qilur. Ana o`shalarga xorlovchi azob bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,110]}]}

{"text":"10. Va ortlarida jahannam bor. \nUlarga kasb qilgan narsalari ham, \nAllohni qo`yib tutgan do`stlari ham hech bir narsada asqotmas. Ularga ulkan azob bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,157]}]}

{"text":"11. Bu (Qur'on) hidoyatdir. Robbilari oyatlariga kufr keltirganlarga alamli azobning ashaddiysi bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,103]}]}

{"text":"12. Alloh sizga dengizni unda O`z amri bilan kemalar yurishi uchun va siz Uning fazlidan istashingiz uchun bo`ysundirib qo`ydi. Shoyadki, shukr keltirsangiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,157]}]}

{"text":"13. Va sizga osmonlardagi narsalarni va \nyerdagi narsalarni  hammasini O`z tomonidan \nbo`ysundirib qo`ydi. Albatta, ana shunda tafakkur qiladigan qavm uchun oyat(belgi)lar bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,180]}]}

{"text":"14. Sen iymon keltirganlarga ayt. \nAllohning kunlaridan umidvor bo`lmaydiganlarni kechirsinlar. Toki, U zot bu qavmni kasb qilib yurgan narsalari uchun mukofotlasin.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,165]}]}

{"text":"15. Kim solih amal qilsa, o`ziga foyda. \nKim yomonlik qilsa, o`ziga zarar. \nSo`ngra Robbingizga qaytarilursiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,110]}]}

{"text":"16. Batahqiq, Biz Bani Isroilga kitobni, 
hukmni va Payg`ambarlikni berdik, 
ularga pok narsalarni rizq qilib berdik va
 ularni olamlar ichida afzal qildik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,156]}]}

{"text":"17. Va Biz ularga (din) ishi haqida ochiq-oydin bayonotlar berdik. Bas, ular o`zlariga ilm kelganidan so`ng o`zaro hasad-adovat qilibgina ixtilofga tushdilar. Albatta, Robbing qiyomat kuni ular orasida ixtilof qilgan narsalari haqida hukm chiqarur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,248]}]}

{"text":"18. So`ngra Biz seni (din) ishida bir shariatga yo`lladik. Bas, unga ergash, bilmaydiganlarning havoyi nafslariga ergashma.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,123]}]}

{"text":"19. Albatta, ular sendan Alloh tomonidan 
bo`ladigan hech bir narsani arita olmaslar. 
Va, albatta, zolimlar bir-birlariga do`stdirlar. 
Alloh taqvodorlarning do`stidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,169]}]}

{"text":"20. Bu (Qur'on) odamlar uchun qalb ko`zlari, \naniq ishonadigan qavm uchun hidoyat va rahmatdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,95]}]}

{"text":"21. Nahotki, yomonliklarni qilganlar ularni \niymon keltirib, solih amallar qilganlarga o`xshash qilmog`imizni, hayotlari ham, mamotlari ham barobar bo`lishini gumon qilsalar?! Ularning qilgan hukmi naqadar ham yomon!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,216]}]}

{"text":"22. Alloh osmonlaru yerni haq ila, har bir jon qilgan kasbiga yarasha, zulm qilinmagan holida jazosi \n(ajri)ni olishi uchun yaratgan.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,133]}]}

{"text":"23. Ayting-chi, havoyi nafsini iloh qilib olgan, 
Alloh uni bilib turib zalolatga solgan va qulog`iga hamda qalbiga muhr bosib, ko`ziga parda tortib 
qo`ygan kimsani Allohdan boshqa kim hidoyat 
qila oladir?! Eslamaysizlarmi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,226]}]}

{"text":"24. Ular: U (hayot) faqat bu dunyodagi hayotimizdir. \nO`lamiz, tirilamiz, bizni faqat zamon halok qiladi, derlar. Ularning bu haqda ilmlari yo`q.\n Ular faqat gumon qiladilar, xolos.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,183]}]}

{"text":"25. Ularga ochiq-oydin oyatlarimiz tilovat qilingan chog`da, ularning: Agar rostgo`y bo`lsangiz, \nota-bobolarimizni keltiring-chi?!  deyishdan boshqa hujjatlari bo`lmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,172]}]}

{"text":"26. Sen: Alloh sizlarni tiriltirur, 
so`ngra o`ldirur, so`ngra sizlarni (bo`lishida) 
shubha yo`q qiyomat kunida jamlar. 
Lekin odamlarning ko`plari bilmaslar, deb ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,170]}]}

{"text":"27. Va osmonlaru yerning mulki Allohnikidir. \nSoat(qiyomat) qoim bo`ladigan kunda, \no`sha kunda botilchilar ziyon torturlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,124]}]}

{"text":"28. Har bir ummatni tiz cho`kkan holida ko`rursan. 
Har bir ummat o`z nomai a'moliga chaqirilur: 
Bugungi kunda qilib yurgan amallaringizning 
jazosi (ajri)ni olursiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,169]}]}

{"text":"29. Mana bu kitobimiz sizga haqni nutq qilur. \nAlbatta, Biz qilgan amalingizni yozib turgan edik (deyilur).","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,99]},{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[99,109]}]}

{"text":"30. Bas, iymon keltirib solih amallarni \nqilganlarni Robbilari O`z rahmatiga kiritur. \nAna o`shaning o`zi ochiq-oydin yutuqdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,127]}]}

{"text":"31. Ammo kufr keltirganlarga esa: \nAxir, sizga Mening oyatlarim tilovat qilinmaganmidi?! Bas, siz mutakabbirlik qildingiz va jinoyatchi \nqavm bo`ldingiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,154]}]}

{"text":"32. Vaqtiki: Albatta, Allohning va'dasi haqdir va 
soat (qiyomat)da shubha yo`qdir, deyilsa, 
Soat(qiyomat) nima ekanini bilmasmiz. 
Biz faqat gumon qilamiz, xolos. 
Biz aniq ishonguvchi emasmiz, dedingiz (deyilur).","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,220]}]}

{"text":"33. Va ularga qilgan amallarining \nyomonliklari ayon bo`ldi va ularni o`zlari \nistehzo qilib yurgan narsa o`rab oldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,117]}]}

{"text":"34. Bugungi kunda xuddi siz ushbu \nkuningizga ro`baro` bo`lishni unutganingizdek, \nBiz ham sizni unuturmiz. Joyingiz jahannamdir va sizlarga hech yordamchilar yo`q.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,165]}]}

{"text":"35. Bunday bo`lishingiz, albatta, sizning Allohning oyatlarini masxara qilib olganingiz va sizni dunyo hayoti g`ururga ketkazgani uchundir, deyildi. \nBas, bugungi kunda ular u(jahannam)dan chiqarilmaslar va ular itobga ham qaytarilmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,239]}]}

{"text":"36. Bas, barcha hamd osmonlarning Robbiga, yerning Robbiga va olamlarning Robbigadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,85]}]}

{"text":"37. Osmonlaru yerdagi ulug`lik Unikidir. \nU zot Aziyzu Hakiymdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,65]}]}
